### JARVIS API Test Suite — US-Compatible
### REST Client extension required (Huachao Mao)
### Click "Send Request" above any ### to test

###############################################
# KRAKEN — US-friendly, CORS-enabled, free
###############################################

### 1. BTC Current Price
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/Ticker?pair=XBTUSD

###

### 2. ETH Current Price
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/Ticker?pair=ETHUSD

###

### 3. BTC + ETH Together
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/Ticker?pair=XBTUSD,ETHUSD

###

### 4. BTC 1h Candles (interval=60 means 60 minutes)
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/OHLC?pair=XBTUSD&interval=60

###

### 5. ETH 1h Candles
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/OHLC?pair=ETHUSD&interval=60

###

### 6. BTC Daily Candles (interval=1440 = 1 day)
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/OHLC?pair=XBTUSD&interval=1440

###

### 7. ETH Daily Candles
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/OHLC?pair=ETHUSD&interval=1440

###

### 8. BTC 4h Candles (interval=240)
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/OHLC?pair=XBTUSD&interval=240

###

### 9. Kraken Server Time (quick connectivity check)
GET https://api.kraken.com/0/public/Time

###############################################
# ALTERNATIVE.ME — Fear & Greed (works fine)
###############################################

### 10. Fear & Greed Index
GET https://api.alternative.me/fng/?limit=1

###

### 11. Fear & Greed — 7 day history
GET https://api.alternative.me/fng/?limit=7

###############################################
# COINBASE — US-friendly backup price source
###############################################

### 12. BTC Price (Coinbase)
GET https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/BTC-USD/spot

###

### 13. ETH Price (Coinbase)
GET https://api.coinbase.com/v2/prices/ETH-USD/spot

